title: LF Silvers to ranked with
body: Looking for a support or jungler mainly to play ranked with, add me Lost Az Fish

replies.body: Added you :) made G5 in the Jungle last season but haven't played this season really so will most likely be deadweight. rookie92

Added. Keen for games later on.

S5 support main.

Did you know that when you queue in ranked Riot will automatically put you with 4 other silvers to play ranked with! How cool is that!

if you wanted to play with someone who's a bit of a troll, feel free to add me.
